   * source/vm/macro.c
      * compiler reports error on the following syntax now (Clipper
        compatibility):
         {|| &macrovar <operator> anysymbol}
        "codeblock contains both macro and declared symbol reference"
        Notice, that Clipper reports error even in this case:
        MEMVAR mvar
        {|| &mvar,mvar}
         
